com.android.uiautomator.common.helpers

Class TimePickerHelper

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.android.uiautomator.common.helpers.TimePickerHelper

  • public class TimePickerHelper
extends java.lang.Object
    Use this helper anywhere there is a time picker to manage. This helper will set time specified in a Calendar object.
